.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302156&d=aauSO5M1qLMrxK%2FXnFuwezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=75113689\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F20302156&h=32c249ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180211/20302156</a><br />\n<br />\n口罩明的4年巴士車長生涯中曾發生多次意外，<br />\n當中最嚴重是2014年的一宗巴士失控掃欄意外<br />\n<br />\n九巴埋站急速轉彎掃鐵欄<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140803/18820439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140803%2F18820439&d=aauSO5M1qLMrxK%2FXnFuwezCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=af8e872e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140803%2F18820439&h=67b2d2bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140803/18820439</a><br />\n<br />\n事後姓鍾乘客不滿車長駕駛態度，「我腳痛都落去鬧個巴士佬，離晒譜！」<br />\n鍾又形容意外時車速很快，疑因此釀意外，<br />\n「入停車場左搖右擺，（轉彎）起碼40、50公里（時速）」。"},{"pid":"f60fa1ca20856d167806cc15033346a2b1a66b42","tid":560003,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32c11dab35306624a0445c9651b7937bad5f1c75","tid":560003,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246fdf07a409ec850ea76574e558069fe1e54582","tid":560003,"uid":1473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"巴士唔係有車cam 咩？ <br />\n到時咪知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"我都覺得好奇怪點解發生咁大件事<br />\n咁耐都仲未有車cam"},{"pid":"a43779f5a0e7a01b67c63dcc85a248f6f48314ee","tid":560003,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c11dab35306624a0445c9651b7937bad5f1c75","tid":560003,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246fdf07a409ec850ea76574e558069fe1e54582","tid":560003,"uid":1473,"like":0,"